data.name: Tyrant Dino Fusion
data.desc: Fusion Summon 1 "Dinowrestler" monster from your Extra Deck, using monsters you control as Fusion Material. If you do, the first time that face-up monster on the field would be destroyed by battle or card effect, it is not destroyed.
